<div class="container mt-4">
    <div class="jumbotron bg-light p-5 rounded">
        <h1 class="display-4">About ABC RETAIL</h1>
        <p class="lead">Driven by Excellence, Committed to Service</p>
        <hr class="my-4">
        <p>
            ABC RETAIL is a premier car and motorbike dealership with a passion for providing top-notch vehicles and unparalleled customer service. Founded on the principles of trust, integrity, and a commitment to customer satisfaction, we have grown to become a trusted name in the automotive industry. Our ability to source any brand of car or motorbike at the best prices nationwide is our promise to you.
        </p>
    </div>

    <div class="row mt-5">
        <div class="col-md-6">
            <h2>Our Mission</h2>
            <p>
                At ABC RETAIL, our mission is simple: to make the process of buying a new car or motorbike as easy and stress-free as possible. We aim to provide a wide range of options, competitive pricing, and expert advice to help our customers make the best choices for their needs.
            </p>
        </div>
        <div class="col-md-6">
            <h2>Our Values</h2>
            <ul class="list-unstyled">
                <li><i class="bi bi-star-fill text-primary"></i> Customer-Centric Approach</li>
                <li><i class="bi bi-star-fill text-primary"></i> Transparency and Integrity</li>
                <li><i class="bi bi-star-fill text-primary"></i> Commitment to Excellence</li>
                <li><i class="bi bi-star-fill text-primary"></i> Passion for Innovation</li>
            </ul>
        </div>
    </div>

    <div class="row mt-5">
        <div class="col-md-4">
            <h3>Our Services</h3>
            <p>
                We offer a comprehensive range of services including new car and motorbike sales, financing options, and a special order service that ensures you get the vehicle you want, when you want it.
            </p>
        </div>
        <div class="col-md-4">
            <h3>Our Team</h3>
            <p>
                Our team is composed of automotive experts and enthusiasts who are dedicated to helping you find the perfect vehicle. We are here to provide you with honest advice and support throughout your buying journey.
            </p>
        </div>
        <div class="col-md-4">
            <h3>Customer Testimonials</h3>
            <p>
                Don’t just take our word for it—hear what our satisfied customers have to say! Visit our <a href="/Testimonials">Testimonials</a> page to read their stories and learn why ABC RETAIL is the best choice for your automotive needs.
            </p>
        </div>
    </div>

    <div class="row mt-5">
        <div class="col-md-12">
            <h2>Why Choose Us?</h2>
            <p>
                At ABC RETAIL, we are more than just a dealership. We are a partner in your journey to finding the perfect vehicle. Our ability to source any brand, combined with our commitment to providing the best prices and outstanding customer service, sets us apart from the competition. Whether you’re looking for a luxury car, a reliable family vehicle, or a sleek motorbike, we have the knowledge and resources to make it happen.
            </p>
        </div>
    </div>

    <div class="row mt-5">
        <div class="col-md-6">
        </div>
        <div class="col-md-6">
        </div>
    </div>
